{"id":130042,"type":4,"name":"LEGO Marvel Super Heroes","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a9/3f/130042_k09GK.jpg","rating":{"total":11,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":2,"6":2,"7":4,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.3},"summary":"《乐高漫威超级英雄》是一款以漫威漫画英雄主打的动作游戏，将囊括Marvel旗下诸多漫画英雄角色，以乐高独特的模型重新架构一个具有科幻和冒险色彩的世界，其中将有8个最具标志性的场景，分别来自于《X战警》《绿巨人》《钢铁侠》《蜘蛛侠》等作品。\r\n在《乐高漫威超级英雄》中，玩家可解锁100多名角色，诸如黑寡妇，鹰眼，死侍等，包含超帅的角色技能，史诗般的打斗场景，解谜元素，当然还有乐高惯有的幽默。玩家将勇敢地承担起拯救世界的终极使命，而玩家也可以在乐高纽约游览那些著名的地标性建筑，同时在地球以外的漫威宇宙中进行大冒险。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>乐高 漫威 超级英雄</li><li><span>开发: </span><a href=\"/person/39322\">TT Games</a></li><li><span>发行: </span><a href=\"/person/34480\">Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment</a></li><li><span>平台: </span>PS3</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>XBOX360</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PSV</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PS4</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">平台: </span>PC</li><li><span>游戏类型: </span>ACT</li><li><span>游玩人数: </span>1</li><li><span>发行日期: </span>2013年10月22日</li>","collection":{"wish":2,"collect":15,"on_hold":2,"dropped":4},"tags":[{"name":"PC","count":2},{"name":"AAVG","count":1},{"name":"PS4","count":1},{"name":"STEAM","count":1},{"name":"3DS","count":1},{"name":"ACT","count":1},{"name":"PS3","count":1}],"crt":[{"id":83181,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/77/7f/83181_crt_ei99Z.jpg","name":"美国队长","desc":"主角"}],"staff":[{"id":39322,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/27/25/39322_prsn_5M5rZ.jpg","name":"TT Games","desc":"开发"},{"id":34480,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/36/14/34480_prsn_SY4g8.jpg","name":"华纳兄弟互动娱乐","desc":"发行"}],"relations":[{"id":215180,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/a6/90/215180_NUh3G.jpg","title":"LEGO Marvel Super Heroes 2","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/215180"},{"id":263346,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/01/ed/263346_arvV6.jpg","title":"LEGO Marvel's Avengers","type":"资料片、外传","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/263346"}]}